{
  "stem": "22892.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Even though you know-- there was-- I was near the area where I was born.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So there was actually an order-- Stalin-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Stalin's order, that anybody wants to leave could do that who was a Polish citizen.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I hoped that my brothers would do the same.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we started writing, and he says that-- wait for me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He says, I will also do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Abraham said that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Well, I waited and waited.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They arrested me once, and they locked me up a second time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, you know-- I finally decided that I can't stay any longer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I had to leave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was a man who was dating one of the women that I was staying with.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he wanted to take charge of me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He'd lost his family, and he saw that this kid, this-- You know, I'd been drinking, I'd been wheeling and dealing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So occasionally I was doing that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he just wanted to be-- to take charge, and he'd be like my father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Well, I liked the man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You know, we did things together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But I didn't want him to take over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But he left Rowne the same time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He says, you come with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I said, fine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We went to Poland together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "From Poland, he had an opportunity to go to Italy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I could go maybe from Poland, later on, maybe to Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You know, somewhere out west.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "From there, you could maybe go to the United States or Palestine-- at that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I came to- yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The second time when I came to the post office, I needed a document that I-- that I-- a birth certificate.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't have anything on me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they made-- they have written one up, and they put a stamp.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
